  <brief_title>People Living With HIV/AIDS, Nitrate, Endotelial Function, Exercise Performance and Muscle Oxygenation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effect of Ingestion of Beet Juice on Endothelial Function, Oxygenation and Muscular Performance in People Living With HIV / AIDS Using Antiretroviral Therapy</official_title>
